description: React component for managing Confluence Spaces, allowing users to search and create spaces via the unified tools proxy API.

methods.name: search
methods.description: Asynchronously invokes the 'search_spaces' tool via API, updating state with the results or error message.

methods.name: create
methods.description: Asynchronously invokes the 'create_space' tool via API, updating state with the result or error message.
